---
---
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8"/>
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
<title>Arts by Justin — Art With a Purpose</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,400;0,700;1,400&family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
<style>
*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box;}
:root{
  --black:#080808;--dark:#111;--card:#161616;
  --gold:#c9a84c;--gold-light:#e8c97a;
  --white:#f0f0f0;--gray:#777;--gray2:#aaa;
}
html{scroll-behavior:smooth;}
body{background:var(--black);color:var(--white);font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;overflow-x:hidden;}
nav{position:fixed;top:0;left:0;right:0;z-index:100;padding:1.2rem 3rem;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;background:rgba(8,8,8,0.92);backdrop-filter:blur(20px);border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.04);}
.logo{font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:1.3rem;letter-spacing:2px;}
.logo span{color:var(--gold);}
.nav-links{display:flex;gap:2rem;list-style:none;}
.nav-links a{color:var(--gray2);text-decoration:none;font-size:0.78rem;letter-spacing:1.5px;text-transform:uppercase;transition:color 0.3s;}
.nav-links a:hover{color:var(--gold);}
.nav-cta{background:var(--gold);color:var(--black);padding:0.55rem 1.4rem;font-size:0.75rem;letter-spacing:1.5px;text-transform:uppercase;font-weight:700;border:none;cursor:pointer;transition:all 0.3s;}
.nav-cta:hover{background:var(--gold-light);}
.hero{height:100vh;position:relative;display:flex;align-items:center;overflow:hidden;}
.hero-painting{position:absolute;right:0;top:0;bottom:0;width:58%;overflow:hidden;}
.hero-painting img{width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center;filter:brightness(0.75);}
.hero-fade{position:absolute;inset:0;background:linear-gradient(to right,#080808 30%,rgba(8,8,8,0.5) 60%,rgba(8,8,8,0.1) 100%);}
.hero-content{position:relative;z-index:2;padding:0 3rem;max-width:600px;}
.hero-eyebrow{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:0.8rem;margin-bottom:2rem;}
.hero-line{width:30px;height:1px;background:var(--gold);}
.hero-eyebrow span{font-size:0.68rem;letter-spacing:4px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--gold);}
.hero h1{font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:clamp(3.2rem,5.5vw,5.5rem);line-height:1.05;margin-bottom:1.5rem;font-weight:700;}
.hero h1 em{color:var(--gold);font-style:italic;display:block;}
.hero-sub{color:var(--gray2);font-size:0.97rem;line-height:1.9;margin-bottom:2.5rem;font-weight:300;max-width:420px;}
.hero-btns{display:flex;gap:1rem;flex-wrap:wrap;}
.btn-gold{background:var(--gold);color:var(--black);padding:0.85rem 2rem;font-size:0.78rem;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;font-weight:700;border:none;cursor:pointer;transition:all 0.3s;}
.btn-gold:hover{background:var(--gold-light);transform:translateY(-2px);}
.btn-ghost{background:transparent;color:var(--white);padding:0.85rem 2rem;font-size:0.78rem;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);cursor:pointer;transition:all 0.3s;}
.btn-ghost:hover{border-color:var(--gold);color:var(--gold);}
.hero-caption{position:absolute;bottom:1.8rem;right:2rem;font-size:0.65rem;letter-spacing:3px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.3);text-transform:uppercase;z-index:2;}
.scroll-hint{position:absolute;bottom:2.5rem;left:3rem;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:1rem;color:var(--gray);font-size:0.68rem;letter-spacing:3px;text-transform:uppercase;}
.scroll-line{width:40px;height:1px;background:var(--gold);animation:grow 2s ease-in-out infinite;}
@keyframes grow{0%,100%{width:40px;opacity:0.4;}50%{width:65px;opacity:1;}}
.img-placeholder{display:flex;align-items:flex-end;justify-content:flex-start;padding:1rem;font-size:0.6rem;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.25);width:100%;height:100%;}
.strip{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(5,1fr);height:260px;gap:2px;}
.strip-item{overflow:hidden;position:relative;cursor:pointer;}
.strip-item .bg{width:100%;height:100%;transition:transform 0.6s,filter 0.4s;filter:brightness(0.65) saturate(0.8);}
.strip-item:hover .bg{transform:scale(1.08);filter:brightness(0.9) saturate(1.2);}
.strip-caption{position:absolute;bottom:0;left:0;right:0;padding:0.8rem;background:linear-gradient(to top,rgba(0,0,0,0.85),transparent);transform:translateY(100%);transition:transform 0.3s;}
.strip-item:hover .strip-caption{transform:translateY(0);}
.strip-caption span{font-size:0.65rem;letter-spacing:1.5px;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.85);}
.about{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;min-height:650px;}
.about-img{position:relative;overflow:hidden;}
.about-img .bg{width:100%;height:100%;}
.about-img-overlay{position:absolute;inset:0;background:linear-gradient(to right,transparent 60%,#111 100%);}
.about-badge{position:absolute;top:2rem;left:2rem;background:var(--gold);color:var(--black);font-size:0.62rem;letter-spacing:3px;text-transform:uppercase;padding:0.4rem 1rem;font-weight:700;}
.about-body{padding:5rem 4rem;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center;background:#111;}
.label{font-size:0.68rem;letter-spacing:4px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--gold);margin-bottom:0.8rem;}
.bar{width:50px;height:2px;background:var(--gold);margin-bottom:2rem;}
.about-body h2{font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:2.4rem;line-height:1.2;margin-bottom:1.5rem;}
.about-body p{color:var(--gray2);font-size:0.93rem;line-height:1.9;margin-bottom:1rem;font-weight:300;}
.pull-quote{margin:1.8rem 0;padding:1.5rem 1.5rem;border-left:2px solid var(--gold);background:rgba(201,168,76,0.05);}
.pull-quote p{font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-style:italic;color:var(--gold-light);font-size:1.05rem;line-height:1.7;}
.works{padding:6rem 3rem;background:var(--black);}
.works-hdr{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:flex-end;margin-bottom:2.5rem;}
.works-hdr h2{font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:2.2rem;}
.masonry{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1.5fr 1fr 1fr;grid-template-rows:320px 280px;gap:3px;}
.art{position:relative;overflow:hidden;cursor:pointer;}
.art .bg{width:100%;height:100%;transition:transform 0.6s,filter 0.4s;filter:brightness(0.8);}
.art:hover .bg{transform:scale(1.06);filter:brightness(1);}
.art-info{position:absolute;bottom:0;left:0;right:0;padding:1.2rem 1.5rem;background:linear-gradient(to top,rgba(0,0,0,0.92),transparent);transform:translateY(100%);transition:transform 0.35s;}
.art:hover .art-info{transform:translateY(0);}
.art-info h3{font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:0.95rem;margin-bottom:0.2rem;}
.art-info p{font-size:0.7rem;letter-spacing:1px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--gray2);}
.art-tag{position:absolute;top:1rem;left:1rem;background:rgba(8,8,8,0.7);font-size:0.6rem;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;padding:0.3rem 0.7rem;color:var(--gold);border:1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.3);}
.span-row{grid-row:span 2;}
.cats{padding:5rem 3rem;background:#111;}
.cats-intro{text-align:center;margin-bottom:3rem;}
.cats-intro h2{font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:2.2rem;margin-bottom:0.8rem;}
.cats-intro p{color:var(--gray2);font-size:0.9rem;font-weight:300;}
.cat-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);gap:2px;}
.cat{position:relative;aspect-ratio:2/3;overflow:hidden;cursor:pointer;}
.cat .bg{width:100%;height:100%;transition:transform 0.6s,filter 0.4s;filter:brightness(0.45) saturate(0.7);}
.cat:hover .bg{transform:scale(1.06);filter:brightness(0.65) saturate(1);}
.cat-info{position:absolute;inset:0;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:flex-end;padding:1.8rem;background:linear-gradient(to top,rgba(0,0,0,0.9) 0%,transparent 60%);}
.cat-info h3{font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:1.2rem;margin-bottom:0.3rem;}
.cat-info span{font-size:0.65rem;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--gold);}
.mag{padding:6rem 3rem;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0d0800,#130900);display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:5rem;align-items:center;}
.mag-card{background:#111;border:1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.15);padding:3rem;position:relative;}
.mag-card::before{content:'';position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;height:3px;background:linear-gradient(to right,var(--gold),var(--gold-light),var(--gold));}
.mag-badge{display:inline-block;background:var(--gold);color:var(--black);font-size:0.62rem;letter-spacing:3px;padding:0.35rem 1rem;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:1.5rem;}
.mag-title{font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:1.9rem;font-style:italic;color:var(--gold-light);line-height:1.2;margin-bottom:0.4rem;}
.mag-date{color:var(--gray);font-size:0.72rem;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:1.5rem;}
.mag-body{color:var(--gray2);font-size:0.88rem;line-height:1.85;margin-bottom:2rem;}
.mag-link{color:var(--gold);font-size:0.75rem;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;text-decoration:none;}
.mag-link:hover{color:var(--gold-light);}
.comm{padding:6rem 3rem;background:var(--black);text-align:center;}
.comm h2{font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:2.5rem;margin-bottom:1rem;}
.comm-sub{color:var(--gray2);max-width:540px;margin:0 auto 3.5rem;font-size:0.93rem;line-height:1.85;font-weight:300;}
.steps{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);gap:1px;margin-bottom:3.5rem;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.04);}
.step{padding:2.5rem 1.5rem;background:var(--black);text-align:left;transition:background 0.3s;}
.step:hover{background:#0d0d0d;}
.step-n{font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:3.5rem;color:rgba(201,168,76,0.1);line-height:1;margin-bottom:1rem;}
.step h4{font-size:0.75rem;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:0.6rem;}
.step p{color:var(--gray);font-size:0.8rem;line-height:1.7;}
.stats-band{padding:5rem 3rem;background:#111;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;gap:4rem;}
.stats-text{max-width:480px;}
.stats-text h2{font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:2.1rem;margin-bottom:1rem;}
.stats-text p{color:var(--gray2);font-size:0.93rem;line-height:1.9;font-weight:300;margin-bottom:2rem;}
.stats-nums{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:2.5rem;flex-shrink:0;}
.stat{text-align:center;}
.stat-n{font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:3rem;color:var(--gold);line-height:1;}
.stat-l{font-size:0.65rem;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--gray);margin-top:0.5rem;}
.testi{padding:5rem 3rem;background:var(--black);text-align:center;}
.testi h2{font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:2rem;margin-bottom:3rem;}
.testi-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:1.5rem;}
.testi-card{background:var(--card);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);padding:2.5rem;text-align:left;}
.stars{color:var(--gold);font-size:0.85rem;letter-spacing:3px;margin-bottom:1rem;}
.testi-q{font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-style:italic;font-size:0.98rem;line-height:1.75;color:var(--white);margin-bottom:1.5rem;}
.testi-by{font-size:0.7rem;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--gray);}
.shop{padding:6rem 3rem;background:#111;}
.shop-top{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:4rem;align-items:center;margin-bottom:3.5rem;}
.shop-top h2{font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:2.2rem;margin-bottom:1rem;}
.shop-top p{color:var(--gray2);font-size:0.93rem;line-height:1.85;font-weight:300;}
.shop-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);gap:1px;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.04);}
.shop-card{padding:2.2rem 2.5rem;background:#111;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;cursor:pointer;transition:background 0.3s;}
.shop-card:hover{background:#1a1a1a;}
.shop-n{font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:1.15rem;margin-bottom:0.3rem;}
.shop-d{color:var(--gray);font-size:0.8rem;}
.shop-arr{color:var(--gold);font-size:1.3rem;transition:transform 0.3s;}
.shop-card:hover .shop-arr{transform:translateX(6px);}
.cta{padding:8rem 3rem;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0d0800,#150900);text-align:center;}
.cta h2{font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:clamp(2.5rem,5vw,4rem);margin-bottom:1.5rem;line-height:1.15;}
.cta h2 em{color:var(--gold);font-style:italic;}
.cta p{color:var(--gray2);font-size:0.98rem;margin-bottom:3rem;font-weight:300;line-height:1.8;}
footer{background:#040404;padding:4rem 3rem;display:grid;grid-template-columns:2fr 1fr 1fr 1fr;gap:3rem;border-top:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);}
.f-logo{font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:1.2rem;margin-bottom:1rem;display:block;}
.f-logo span{color:var(--gold);}
.f-about{color:var(--gray);font-size:0.8rem;line-height:1.85;max-width:240px;margin-bottom:1.5rem;}
.f-social{display:flex;gap:1.5rem;}
.f-social a{color:var(--gray);text-decoration:none;font-size:0.72rem;letter-spacing:1.5px;text-transform:uppercase;transition:color 0.3s;}
.f-social a:hover{color:var(--gold);}
.f-col h4{font-size:0.68rem;letter-spacing:3px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--gold);margin-bottom:1.5rem;}
.f-col ul{list-style:none;}
.f-col li{margin-bottom:0.8rem;}
.f-col a{color:var(--gray);text-decoration:none;font-size:0.8rem;transition:color 0.3s;}
.f-col a:hover{color:var(--white);}
.f-bottom{background:#020202;padding:1.4rem 3rem;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;color:var(--gray);font-size:0.72rem;border-top:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.03);}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<nav>
  <span class="logo">Arts <span>by</span> Justin</span>
  <ul class="nav-links">
    <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
    <li><a href="/about">The Story</a></li>
    <li><a href="/portfolio">Portfolio</a></li>
    <li><a href="/commissions">Commissions</a></li>
    <li><a href="/press">Press</a></li>
  </ul>
  <button class="nav-cta">Shop Now</button>
</nav>

<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-painting" id="heroPainting"></div>
  <div class="hero-fade"></div>
  <div class="hero-content">
    <div class="hero-eyebrow">
      <div class="hero-line"></div>
      <span>Raleigh, NC · Est. 2020</span>
    </div>
    <h1>Art With<br/>a <em>Purpose.</em></h1>
    <p class="hero-sub">Bold. Expressive. Spirit-led. Original acrylic &amp; mixed media works — created in Raleigh, collected around the world.</p>
    <div class="hero-btns">
      <button class="btn-gold">Explore the Work →</button>
      <button class="btn-ghost">My Story</button>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="hero-caption" id="heroCaption"></div>
  <div class="scroll-hint">
    <div class="scroll-line"></div>
    <span>Scroll</span>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="strip" id="galleryStrip"></div>

<section class="about">
  <div class="about-img" id="aboutImgWrap"></div>
  <div class="about-body">
    <p class="label">The Story</p>
    <div class="bar"></div>
    <h2>From Poverty<br/>to Fine Art</h2>
    <p>My journey didn't start in a studio. It started with a dream bigger than my circumstances — a belief that beauty could exist even in the hardest places.</p>
    <p>Every canvas I touch carries that story. Of faith. Of resilience. Of the conviction that art can change how we see the world and ourselves.</p>
    <div class="pull-quote">
      <p>"I don't just create art. I create conversations, connections, and change."</p>
    </div>
    <br/>
    <button class="btn-gold">Read My Full Story →</button>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="works">
  <div class="works-hdr">
    <div>
      <p class="label">Portfolio</p>
      <div class="bar"></div>
      <h2>Featured Works</h2>
    </div>
    <button class="btn-ghost">View All Work →</button>
  </div>
  <div class="masonry" id="masonryGrid"></div>
</section>

<section class="cats">
  <div class="cats-intro">
    <p class="label" style="text-align:center;">Browse by Theme</p>
    <div class="bar" style="margin:0.5rem auto 1rem;"></div>
    <h2>Every Canvas Tells a Story</h2>
    <p>From sports legends to spiritual journeys — explore Justin's world.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="cat-grid" id="catGrid"></div>
</section>

<section class="mag">
  <div>
    <p class="label">Press &amp; Recognition</p>
    <div class="bar"></div>
    <h2 style="font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:2.2rem;margin-bottom:1.5rem;">Recognized<br/>Beyond the Studio</h2>
    <p style="color:var(--gray2);font-size:0.93rem;line-height:1.9;font-weight:300;margin-bottom:1rem;">Justin's work has earned its place not just on walls — but in publications, galleries, and art shows that celebrate artists who create with purpose and vision.</p>
    <p style="color:var(--gray2);font-size:0.93rem;line-height:1.9;font-weight:300;margin-bottom:2rem;">From Raleigh to international stages, the story keeps growing.</p>
    <button class="btn-gold">View Press &amp; Awards →</button>
  </div>
  <div class="mag-card">
    <span class="mag-badge">Featured Magazine</span>
    <div class="mag-title">From Poverty<br/>to Fine Art</div>
    <div class="mag-date">August 2023</div>
    <p class="mag-body">A full feature on Justin Keishing's remarkable journey from humble beginnings to international recognition — a story of faith, resilience, and art made with purpose.</p>
    <a href="#" class="mag-link">Read the Full Feature →</a>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="comm">
  <p class="label" style="text-align:center;">Work With Justin</p>
  <div class="bar" style="margin:0.5rem auto 1.5rem;"></div>
  <h2>Let's Create Something<br/>Just for You</h2>
  <p class="comm-sub">Have a vision? A story you want told in paint? I take on a limited number of commissioned works each year. Every piece is personal, intentional, and made with purpose.</p>
  <div class="steps">
    <div class="step"><div class="step-n">01</div><h4>Connect</h4><p>Reach out and share your idea, vision, or the story you want told.</p></div>
    <div class="step"><div class="step-n">02</div><h4>Consult</h4><p>We discuss concept, size, medium, timeline, and investment.</p></div>
    <div class="step"><div class="step-n">03</div><h4>Create</h4><p>Justin brings your vision to life with care, intention, and purpose.</p></div>
    <div class="step"><div class="step-n">04</div><h4>Deliver</h4><p>Your one-of-a-kind piece arrives, ready to hang and move people.</p></div>
  </div>
  <button class="btn-gold">Start a Commission →</button>
</section>

<section class="stats-band">
  <div class="stats-text">
    <p class="label">Art Shows</p>
    <div class="bar"></div>
    <h2>Seen Around<br/>the World</h2>
    <p>Because of you — my collectors and supporters — my work has found walls in galleries and art shows internationally. Every show is a reminder of why I create.</p>
    <button class="btn-ghost">See Where I've Shown →</button>
  </div>
  <div class="stats-nums">
    <div class="stat"><div class="stat-n">450+</div><div class="stat-l">Works Created</div></div>
    <div class="stat"><div class="stat-n">26+</div><div class="stat-l">Art Shows</div></div>
    <div class="stat"><div class="stat-n">8+</div><div class="stat-l">Countries</div></div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="testi">
  <p class="label" style="text-align:center;">Collector Stories</p>
  <div class="bar" style="margin:0.5rem auto 1rem;"></div>
  <h2>What Collectors Say</h2>
  <div class="testi-grid">
    <div class="testi-card">
      <div class="stars">★★★★★</div>
      <p class="testi-q">"Justin's work stopped me in my tracks. I walked past it twice before I realized I couldn't leave without it. A year later I still discover something new every day."</p>
      <div class="testi-by">— Collector, New York</div>
    </div>
    <div class="testi-card">
      <div class="stars">★★★★★</div>
      <p class="testi-q">"I commissioned a piece for my office and Justin captured exactly what I described — but more powerfully than I ever imagined. People ask about it every single day."</p>
      <div class="testi-by">— Commission Client, Dallas</div>
    </div>
    <div class="testi-card">
      <div class="stars">★★★★★</div>
      <p class="testi-q">"There's a spirituality in his work that you feel before you understand. I knew I had to own this piece the moment I saw it."</p>
      <div class="testi-by">— Collector, London</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="shop">
  <div class="shop-top">
    <div>
      <p class="label">Collect the Work</p>
      <div class="bar"></div>
      <h2>Take a Piece Home</h2>
      <p>Originals, museum-quality prints, and more — available across multiple platforms so collectors worldwide can find and own Justin's work.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="shop-grid">
    <div class="shop-card"><div><div class="shop-n">Etsy</div><div class="shop-d">Original works &amp; prints</div></div><span class="shop-arr">→</span></div>
